Name: posterior polymorphous corneal dystrophy 1
Definition: A posterior polymorphous corneal dystrophy that has_material_basis_in autosomal dominant inheritance of mutation in the OVOL2 gene on chromosome 20p11.23.

Name: posterior polymorphous corneal dystrophy 2
Definition: A posterior polymorphous corneal dystrophy that has_material_basis_in heterozygous mutation in the COL8A2 gene on chromosome 1p34.3.

Name: posterior polymorphous corneal dystrophy 3
Definition: A posterior polymorphous corneal dystrophy that has_material_basis_in heterozygous mutation in the ZEB1 gene on chromosome 10p11.22.
